race.comment: FERNDALE FLYER (2) overcame a collision to score an effortless Grade 5/6 win at this track over 520m latest, winning by 8 lengths (29.84). Has the ability and looks a key chance again. WEST ON MODEL (6) was out of the placings last time but before that was an impressive winner (29.84) in a OPEN at this track. Has the ability and expected to do much better. BINNAWAY CHARM (1) collided in the run and boxed on to place when a 2.75 lengths second (30.28) in a Grade 5 at this track. Leading player again. UNEQUALLED (7) cannot be left out after placing as public elect last start.
